# CVEs suppressed pending resolution of Alpine CDN TLS failure in k3s cluster.
# The cluster cannot reach dl-cdn.alpinelinux.org so `apk upgrade` cannot be run
# in CI. These packages cannot be patched until the CDN connectivity is restored.
# Track at: MYS-226 (CI/CD infrastructure)

# zlib 1.3.1-r2 → 1.3.2-r0 (arbitrary code execution via buffer overflow in untgz)
CVE-2026-22184

# libexpat 2.7.4-r0 → 2.7.5-r0 (authorization bypass allows arbitrary SQL execution)
CVE-2026-32767
